{"tid":829758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【水果藏針】繼士多啤梨香蕉後 澳超市芒果都有針","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T17:54:30.000Z","uid":150685,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0219bc6a8dc82d8ac151abda7a6241c910a561e2","tid":829758,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180920/large/1537446221_a102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180920%2Flarge%2F1537446221_a102.jpg&h=253cb84b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲士多啤梨遭人藏針的事件不斷擴大，繼士多啤梨、香蕉、蘋果之後，有民眾聲稱在超市買來的芒果之中亦藏有縫紉針。<br />\n<br />\n該名顧客周一在新南威爾斯省戈斯福德(Gosford)的Coles超市買來芒果，兩日後切開卻發現內藏一枚針，隨後已經報警。警方表示︰「警方取走該枚針作化驗，事件中沒人受傷。<br />\n<br />\nColes超市則表示「嚴肅對待食物安全，這次事件正進行調查」，並表示當局建議民眾進食水果之前應先切開。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲警方已接到超過100宗報告，指多種水果之中被人藏針，不過有不少個案是虛報或者是「有樣學樣」。新南威爾斯省一名男童周三被捕，他承認把針藏在士多啤梨中「惡作劇」；西澳一名男童聲稱發現士多啤梨藏針，由於年紀太小，警方不作起訴。<br />\n英國《每日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180920/58703639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58703639&d=h7tbDmTK8csxJeeCU%2Bz0FTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=ccc753ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58703639&h=2ade19c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180920/58703639</a>"},{"pid":"6b52eb1a9376ba125ce5a20eae4ae0bf9a49e90a","tid":829758,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"做乜要咁做？"},{"pid":"bff027c0df9a3f8c0f60eac984a75d52ec7cc4c9","tid":829758,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b52eb1a9376ba125ce5a20eae4ae0bf9a49e90a","tid":829758,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":